  "title": "Vice Principal (Preschool) - North",
  "description": "<h3><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></h3>\n<p>Reporting to the Principal, you will play a key role in shaping the strategic direction and overall management of the preschool.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Contribute to curriculum planning and professional development by providing insights and guidance, and mentoring teachers on pedagogy, teaching methods, and the effective use of tools and resources.</li>\n  <li>Lead the development of strategies for parent engagement, community involvement, and talent management.</li>\n  <li>Oversee and optimize the management of center resources, such as staff scheduling, inventory control, and managing controllable expenses.</li>\n  <li>Implement and manage specific center programs, initiatives, and events.</li>\n  <li>Handle various administrative tasks related to the smooth operation of the center.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Pre-school Education-Leadership (DPL) is a must.</li>\n  <li>Experience: 3-5 years in early childhood education, with 1-2 years in a supervisory role.</li>\n  <li>Familiar with ECDA regulations and EYDF.</li>\n  <li>Strong leadership, communication, and organizational skills.</li>\n  <li>Passionate about child development and early childhood education.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
